_sText:
Skill Surf map with 4 stages.

Spawn - Nikki
Level 1 - Sangre Nueva
Level 2 - Nikki
Level 3 - Sangre Nueva
Level 4 - Nikki
Jail 1 - Sangre Nueva
Jail 2 - Sangre Nueva

The Main Jail has 3 Functions, one of these Functions will be randomly activated by pushing a button in the middle of the Jail. The Winner is able to choose between two special Guns (Fire-Gun or Freeze-Gun).

This map is designed to be played on a Tickrate of 66, Sv_Airaccelerate 150, and Sv_Gravity 800.

Many thanks to all the beta testers!!
- Sharp
- Northern Comfort
- Bigmac
- Maxxie
- Rapsodia
- Shini

- VZero

We are both very happy to release this map for all of our friends I would personally like to thank Sangre Nueva for his tremendous help and support with this map, and his beautiful levels. Without him all of this wouldn't have been possible.
